{"tid":2149803,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"探員到黎智英兒子開設餐廳調查　帶走電腦","createTime":"2020-08-10T15:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T15:07:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"47e568ed55890c89c2d75735bb39ee9f33f562eb","tid":2149803,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T15:01:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542847-20200810.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542847-20200810.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mHfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=d2039b09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542847-20200810.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9cc6bc29\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542847-20200810.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n消息指，壹傳媒集團創辦人黎智英、兩名兒子和4名集團高層被捕。<br />\n<br />\n超過10名探員中午到黎智英次子黎耀恩在中環開設的餐廳調查，現場所見，餐廳內有身穿廚師及侍應裝束的人員在內，見到警方在餐廳內帶走一部電腦。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，黎耀恩涉嫌違反《港區國安法》的勾結罪被捕。"},{"pid":"67887a3e5a4e402a0e2a362f49adb0989b35cb78","tid":2149803,"uid":29153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T15:05:56.000Z","msg":"收銀機？"},{"pid":"e113040b378d5891117fb7171613803a61ab3e23","tid":2149803,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T15:07:21.000Z","msg":"拉埋個廚師丫笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}